text: Toto:Beans! Have you seen my owner?
Beans:Yeah... And I'm waiting for him by the front door
Toto:I think I'll go and ask the other puppies
Beans:Okay, and remember to notify me of any news
Toto:Yes, I have something to tell you!
Toto:Still has the smell of my owner...
Toto:I wonder where did she go...
Toto:But there is no one to play with...
Toto:and ask about what's going on
